list_definition.definition: a girl who likes rough games and activities

list_ex_of_english: She is a bit of a tomboy but loves designer clothes.
She is a tomboy and works as an assistant at a dojo.
She is a tomboy and more easy going than her older sister, which is why she prefers to hang out with the guys.
She is a lively tomboy with strong ideals of love and lawfulness.
Winsome charm is at a minimum; tomboy toughness takes over.
A bit of a tomboy, she means to do well and is not disheartened when others put her down, instead she encourages them.
Growing up with 3 brothers made her more of a tomboy.
She has said that she used to be a tomboy and is a fan of wakeboarding, snowboarding, and soccer.
